entries.s_152: A friend of Orrekazzapirr and Imarrra. Do you know where they are?
entries.s_154: I'm afraid you are too late. They were sold to the Empire to be shipped to their prison on Dathomir. Apparently they knew something they weren't supposed to. I fear they will be tortured to death...
entries.s_156: Not if I can help it! Hang in there, your friends will come for you.
entries.s_158: I hope you are right. Good luck friend!
entries.s_162: Your friends know about this, they will come in greater numbers.
